abstract: M.C. Hammer, the rapper, announced his new search company called WireDoo, at the Web 2.0 Summit. The site hopes to offers "relationship search results."

lead_paragraph: Among the technology entrepreneurs announcing new products at the Web 2.0 Summit in San Francisco, there was an unlikely guest: M.C. Hammer, the rapper.

headline.main: M.C. Hammer Announces WireDoo, a Search Start-Up
